      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Direct-write hot path\n\nsprite.color = (r,g,b,a)\n  \u2192 mesh.writeColor(slot, \u2026)\n  \u2192 markDirty(slot)\n\nO(1), no ECS subscriber, no archetype move.\nO(N slots) once per frame to flush.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "callout-2",
      "originalText": "Direct-write hot path\n\nsprite.color = (r,g,b,a)\n  \u2192 mesh.writeColor(slot, \u2026)\n  \u2192 markDirty(slot)\n\nO(1), no ECS subscriber, no archetype move.\nO(N slots) once per frame to flush.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12,
      "index": "aZ"
    },
