    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "shader-code",
      "x": 56.69183783844778,
      "y": 1665.197850307524,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 262.5,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1072,
      "version": 35,
      "versionNonce": 1662656669,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779046254025,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "const enableFlags = attribute('instanceSystem', 'vec4').w     // per-instance bitmask\n\nlet color = baseColor                                          // from _buildBaseColor()\n\nfor (const { effectClass, bitIndex, attrs } of effectData) {\n  const divisor = float(1 << bitIndex)\n  const shifted = floor(enableFlags.div(divisor))\n  const enabled = mod(shifted, float(2.0))                     // 0.0 or 1.0\n\n  const effectResult = effectClass._node({ inputColor: color, inputUV: atlasUV, attrs })\n\n  color = mix(color, effectResult, enabled)                    // branchless gate\n}\n\nreturn color",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "const enableFlags = attribute('instanceSystem', 'vec4').w     // per-instance bitmask\n\nlet color = baseColor                                          // from _buildBaseColor()\n\nfor (const { effectClass, bitIndex, attrs } of effectData) {\n  const divisor = float(1 << bitIndex)\n  const shifted = floor(enableFlags.div(divisor))\n  const enabled = mod(shifted, float(2.0))                     // 0.0 or 1.0\n\n  const effectResult = effectClass._node({ inputColor: color, inputUV: atlasUV, attrs })\n\n  color = mix(color, effectResult, enabled)                    // branchless gate\n}\n\nreturn color",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12,
      "index": "b0B"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "shader-note",
      "x": 39.63549196337169,
      "y": 1963.796486961299,
      "width": 1170,
      "height": 40,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#7c3aed",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1073,
      "version": 261,
      "versionNonce": 1738933501,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779046254025,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Same compiled shader runs for every sprite in the batch.  enabled = 0 \u2192 mix returns base color;  enabled = 1 \u2192 mix returns effect.\nAll effects are still evaluated, but their contribution is gated by a single MAD \u2014 no dynamic branching, no per-instance pipeline switch.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Same compiled shader runs for every sprite in the batch.  enabled = 0 \u2192 mix returns base color;  enabled = 1 \u2192 mix returns effect.\nAll effects are still evaluated, but their contribution is gated by a single MAD \u2014 no dynamic branching, no per-instance pipeline switch.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12,
      "index": "b0C"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
