      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "\u2460 Setters fire  (per gameplay event)\n\n  sprite.color = \u2026   \u2192   mesh.writeColor(slot, \u2026)\n                       \u2192   tracker.markDirty(slot)\n\n  ~5 ns \u00b7 zero allocs \u00b7 O(1) direct buffer poke",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\u2460 Setters fire  (per gameplay event)\n\n  sprite.color = \u2026   \u2192   mesh.writeColor(slot, \u2026)\n                       \u2192   tracker.markDirty(slot)\n\n  ~5 ns \u00b7 zero allocs \u00b7 O(1) direct buffer poke",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12,
      "index": "b0H"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
