      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "\u2461 Systems run  (per frame, ordered)\n\n  batchAssign \u2192 batchReassign \u2192 batchRemove\n     \u2192 batchSort \u2192 sceneGraphSync \u2192 transformSync\n\n  Factory-closure scratch state per SpriteGroup\n  \u2014 no per-frame Sets, no cross-group bleed.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\u2461 Systems run  (per frame, ordered)\n\n  batchAssign \u2192 batchReassign \u2192 batchRemove\n     \u2192 batchSort \u2192 sceneGraphSync \u2192 transformSync\n\n  Factory-closure scratch state per SpriteGroup\n  \u2014 no per-frame Sets, no cross-group bleed.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12,
      "index": "b0J"
    },
