      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "\u2462 flushDirtyRanges()  (end of frame)\n\n  per attribute:\n    if dirtyBuckets \u2265 threshold \u2192 needsUpdate \u2192 bufferData\n    else                        \u2192 N \u00d7 addUpdateRange (aligned)\n\n  Only the dirty regions cross the bus.\n  Most frames touch < 5 % of the buffer.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\u2462 flushDirtyRanges()  (end of frame)\n\n  per attribute:\n    if dirtyBuckets \u2265 threshold \u2192 needsUpdate \u2192 bufferData\n    else                        \u2192 N \u00d7 addUpdateRange (aligned)\n\n  Only the dirty regions cross the bus.\n  Most frames touch < 5 % of the buffer.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12,
      "index": "b0L"
    },
