      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "\u2460 VRAM upload  (WebGPURenderer)\n\n  bufferData (full, 1 call)   OR\n  bufferSubData \u00d7 N           (one per dirty bucket)\n\n  No per-frame buffer recreation,\n  no map/unmap, no staging copy on the hot path.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\u2460 VRAM upload  (WebGPURenderer)\n\n  bufferData (full, 1 call)   OR\n  bufferSubData \u00d7 N           (one per dirty bucket)\n\n  No per-frame buffer recreation,\n  no map/unmap, no staging copy on the hot path.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12,
      "index": "b0N"
    },
