      "seed": 1214,
      "version": 463,
      "versionNonce": 604543933,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779046265924,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "\u2462 drawIndexed(6, instanceCount)\n\n  VS:  gl_Position = projection \u00d7 view \u00d7 instanceMatrix \u00d7 cornerPos\n       \u2014 instance-rate attribute fetch per slot\n\n  FS:  baseColor (atlas sample + UV flip + tint)\n       for each effect: color = mix(color, eff_i, bit_i)\n       blend / alphaTest",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\u2462 drawIndexed(6, instanceCount)\n\n  VS:  gl_Position = projection \u00d7 view \u00d7 instanceMatrix \u00d7 cornerPos\n       \u2014 instance-rate attribute fetch per slot\n\n  FS:  baseColor (atlas sample + UV flip + tint)\n       for each effect: color = mix(color, eff_i, bit_i)\n       blend / alphaTest",
