      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Two ordering paths on the GPU side:\n\n   \u25b8  Alpha-blend  (default)   depthWrite = false  \u2192  CPU sort by zIndex  (batchSortSystem, in-place swapSlots)\n   \u25b8  alphaTest > 0            depthWrite = true   \u2192  GPU depth test orders fragments; CPU sort skipped\n\nResult: one drawIndexed per batch, one pipeline per material, per-instance state in 6 buffer fetches.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Two ordering paths on the GPU side:\n\n   \u25b8  Alpha-blend  (default)   depthWrite = false  \u2192  CPU sort by zIndex  (batchSortSystem, in-place swapSlots)\n   \u25b8  alphaTest > 0            depthWrite = true   \u2192  GPU depth test orders fragments; CPU sort skipped\n\nResult: one drawIndexed per batch, one pipeline per material, per-instance state in 6 buffer fetches.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12,
      "index": "b0X"
